            <p>You agree to abide by Skillsbd's Trust & Safety policies, Restricted Topics policy, and other course quality standards or policies prescribed by Skillsbd from time to time. You should check these policies periodically to ensure that you comply with any updates to them. You understand that your use of the Services is subject to Skillsbd's approval, which we may grant or deny at our sole discretion.</p>
