            <p>When creating a course, you are advised to select the best price for your course. You may choose any price for your course. Skillsbd being an open platform for instructors who want to create and publish their courses on the platform, promote and practice fair competition. For this reason, while reviewing your course, we might suggest a more appropriate price in cases where your selected course price might severely undercut other instructors similar courses. We do this only to keep off our platform of any unhealthy practices that might impact our students and instructors.</p>
